            <title>[SHINDIG-1215] Honor the maxObjSize in BasicHttpFetcher and make it configurable</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/SHINDIG-1215</link>
                <project id="12310741" key="SHINDIG">Shindig</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Honor the maximum allowed object size when reading the response body of an HTTP request in BasicHttpFetcher.&lt;/p&gt;

